gui.platforms.wrench.edit.remove.info:
On Apply;
  Remove this platform type from the selected area
 If Place is also toggled;
  Platforms of this type but with different textures will be replaced instead

gui.platforms.wrench.edit.place.info:
On Apply;
  Places this platform from inventory into available spaces
 If Remove is also toggled;
  Platforms of this type but with different textures will be replaced instead
